A cyberpunk cityscape at night where countless glowing data streams flow like rivers through dark urban canyons, converging and branching in organic tree-like patterns reminiscent of version control branches. Neon-lit terminals and holographic displays float at various heights, each showing cascading code fragments in electric blue and hot pink. In the foreground, a lone figure in a hooded jacket stands on a platform, arms outstretched, orchestrating the flowing streams of data that spiral around them like luminous threads. The architecture features brutalist concrete structures covered in circuit-board patterns that pulse with soft green light. Rain falls through the scene, creating reflections on wet surfaces that mirror the data streams above. The atmosphere is dense with fog and digital particles, giving depth to the layered composition of merging and diverging light trails.
